snippet.title: Dark and Darker Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Dark and Darker is a first-person fantasy dungeon crawler extraction game, where players take on ruthless monsters, navigate devious traps, and uncover secrets and untold treasures deep within the halls of mountains and crypts. 

Play solo, duo, or trios and take on the nightmares that await, defeating bosses to claim ultimate power, and slaying other adventurers who stand in your way - or form uneasy alliances to increase your odds of surviving the armies of fearsome creatures eager to strike you down.
